  "description": "The entry point. Trefoil at braidDepth 0.30 — just below WEAVE-I — creates a rich, naturally asymmetric chorus that is immediately musical without revealing the full topology character. The directional ring coupling flows in one direction around strands 0-1-2 while strand 3 floats free, a gentle harmonic satellite. LFO1 on braid depth at 0.04 Hz breathes the topology on a 25-second cycle: the coupling crosses WEAVE-I twice per cycle, barely perceptible but alive. The WEAVE macro is the invitation — raise it to enter the knot.",
